        },
        "labels": {
          "scenario.id": "{{scenarioID}}",
          "id": "{{besuContractTxID}}"
        }
      }
      """
    Then the response code should be 202
    When I send "POST" request to "{{global.api}}/transactions/deploy-contract" with json:
      """
